skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: life one hundred point seven
des:
Welcome to Life 100.7! Enable this skill to listen to uplifting music and conversation from Omaha, Nebraska, and the surrounding areas. You’ll hear your favorite artists like TobyMac, MercyMe, Casting Crowns, For King and Country, and more! 
To get started, say “Alexa, enable Life 100.7.” After that, simply say, “Alexa, play Life 100.7.”
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
